“SHADED” THE EP IS AVAILABLE FOR PURCHASE AT NARISSAWORLD.COM RIGHT NOW. 
ALL 4 TRACKS + A DIGITAL BOOKLET FOR $20. 

As an independent artist, I want to sell my digital product directly to my consumer with no middle man FIRST, before making it available to the public for streaming.  I think the streaming industry has me f*d up personally if they think I want a fraction of a penny per stream. That’s not gonna cut it for young hustla like myself. So if you have been rockin wit the movement, I need to see your support. I will have something special for everyone who is PROUD TO PAY.

“SHADED” is a 4 song EP produced by @rottenroseq @yonnydidit and myself. 

You can purchase it for $20 at the link in my bio. It comes with a digital booklet full of exclusive photos and a few special messages from me.
